page.title: 05A Day in the life of Natalie
page.content: Most mornings I get up at about 6.30 a.m. and go downstairs to wash and have my breakfast of sugar puffs. While I get dressed I like to listen to my favourite tape.At about 7.55 we leave in the car to go to my nanas where I catch the school bus. School starts at 9.00am and finishes at 3.20pm. At school we have lessons like Maths, English, Art, Geography and we also play musical instruments.When I get home I have tea and then clean out my guinea pigs water, have a shower do my teeth and go to bed. Before I turn my light out I read a book.
